        <p>
            You go for a swim. The water feels like a solid, and it's hard to stay afloat. This isn't relaxing.
        </p>
        <hr>
        <a href="/forest/pond/side/swim?pov=keep-swimming">
            Keep Swimming
        </a>
        <a href="/forest/pond/side">
            Get Back on Shore
